            "title": "滬指開市升不足1點 深成指跌42點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">內地股市初段變動不大，上證綜指以3924點開市，升不足1點或0.02%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">深證成指開市報13683點，則跌42點或0.31%。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">滬深300指數跌不足1點，開報4491點；創業板指數開市報3247點，跌26點或0.8%。</p>\n</div>",
