            "title": "港股開市︱初段反彈 恒指升67點報24818點 中銀香港績後高開逾2%",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">中東戰火持續，外圍市況受壓，卻未阻港股今早初段反彈。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">恒生指數開市報24818點，升67點或0.27%。恒生科技指數開報4693點，升3點或0.08%；國企指數以8411點開市，升12點或0.15%。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"AP圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股5.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"AP圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/20230808_FI_source-ap_港股5.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">AP圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">藍籌股業績公布高峰期進入尾聲，昨天收市後派成績表的重磅股，今早股價普遍造好。中銀香港(02388)開報41.62元，升2.66%；母企中國銀行(03988)開報4.89元，暫時無升跌。農業銀行(01288)開報5.4元，同樣暫時無升跌。中國神華(01088)開報48元，升0.46%；美的集團(00300)開報81.65元，升4.08%；順豐控股(06936)開報34.26元，升2.82%。</p>\n\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"中銀香港2024年度年報封面\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/02388-2024.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"中銀香港2024年度年報封面\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/704x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/03/02388-2024.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">中銀香港2024年度年報封面</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">其他重磅股亦升多於跌，滙控(00005)開報124.8元，升0.97%；友邦(01299)開報84.75元，跌0.24%。阿里巴巴(09988)開報120.8元，升0.25%；騰訊(00700)開報484.4元，升0.58%；擬發人民幣計價優先票據的京東(09618)，今早開報113.6元，升0.53%。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">另外，今日再有兩隻新股登場，傅里葉(03625)以85.05元開市，較招股價40元高1.13倍；銅師傅(00664)則開報35.42元，較招股價60元低40.97%。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15816222-%e6%b8%af%e8%82%a1%e9%96%8b%e5%b8%82%ef%b8%b1%e5%88%9d%e6%ae%b5%e5%8f%8d%e5%bd%88-%e6%81%92%e6%8c%87%e5%8d%8767%e9%bb%9e%e5%a0%b124818%e9%bb%9e-%e4%b8%ad%e9%8a%80%e9%a6%99%e6%b8%af%e7%b8%be%e5%be%8c",
            "image": "https://image.bastillepost.com/704x369/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/04/HKSTOCK.jpg.webp",
            "pub_date": "2026-03-31 09:31:31",
