            "title": "常達控股、多想雲停牌",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\" style=\"font-weight: 400;\">常達控股(01433)、多想雲(06696)今早上午9時起暫停買賣。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15816174-%e5%b8%b8%e9%81%94%e6%8e%a7%e8%82%a1%e3%80%81%e5%a4%9a%e6%83%b3%e9%9b%b2%e5%81%9c%e7%89%8c",
